metadata.name: MAAC #2153
metadata.description:
This micro collection contains Mutant AI Art Club members which will contain a unique utility in form of a physical copy of the MAAC. 

Each holder of a physical MAAC will be enabled to get 
- a signed physical copy of the NFT either as
  * a poster,
  * printed canvas or
  * framed image
  with a minimum size of 40x40cm.
- 1 airdrop spot for the upcoming MAAC collection of over 5000 unique items
- 5 whitelist places (for you and 4 friends) for the presale

After buying please contact via twitter: https://twitter.com/ai_mutants
